In today’s video, I’m breaking down the top 20 fantasy books that aged the worst — and the ones that aged the best.
Some stories fall apart when revisited years later, whether due to outdated themes, weak craft, or cultural shifts. Others remain genuinely timeless. But WHYYYYYYYY????
And yes… we need to talk about Terry Goodkind.

This is a deep dive into what separates stories that last from those that don’t.
